title: Pearl Jam 2005 Official Bootlegs
description:
"Pearl Jam took a year-long touring break until the 2004 Vote for Change tour, but the band elected not to release bootlegs for the six shows from that tour. The band took yet another year off until a fall 2005 tour of Canada and South America. For the first time, the bootlegs were MP3-only (CBR 192kbps), only available through the band's official website."
